    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per design.md §3.3 Email association is HIGH-tier (~863 LOC). It drives email→matter routing,
      which is a user-visible automation. Per §2.3, Communications-related test files have the
      HIGHEST sibling-coordination risk in this project — the x-email-communication-solution-r2
      project is actively modifying nearby code. This task is HIGH-tier so it stays in scope, but
      coordination is mandatory before non-trivial edits.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="014" status="not-started">Compile health verified</dependency>
    </dependencies>
